### Container Level Variables §

Container level variables have static lifetime and are order-independent and lazily analyzed. The initialization value of container level variables is implicitly comptime . If a container level variable is `const` then its value is `comptime` \-known, otherwise it is runtime-known. test\_container\_level\_variables.zig

